    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is something that can be useful, for sure. I'm not sure I'd like this as part of the core widgets (a calendar library is a project by itself).\n\nMaybe we should just provide the default widget that will work with HTML5 date elements, and show a few examples of plugging external calendar libraries (jQuery, etc).\n",
