    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Actually I think a widget able to do numerical refinement and manipulate/display date from timestamp should be in the core widgets to address all the media/news use cases.\nIf we talk about predefined range, it also make sens to propose a manual range where the calendar seems to be the right UI element.\n\nThis could be the really mandatory widget:\n![screenshot 2015-10-18 21 55 22](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/976175/10609358/972d2a06-7743-11e5-94e8-0700731f7564.png)\n",
